result.notes:
Personal records from Lin Baldock. 
     List made up of from a number of visits to the site over the last year (list not complete as of 08/06/06). This list illustrates 'rather unusual algal community with the notable occurrance of the very rare filamentous red seaweed Ceramium circinatum. Of about eight samples of Ceramium species collected, about 5 were confirmed as C.circinatum. which suggests that it is doing fairly well at the site' - LB
